name: Mt. Prau | Dronephotography #1
description:
Mount Prau has a stunning view, especially at sunrise. The peak of Mount Prau is a vast meadow that extends from west to east. Mountain with a height of about 2,565 meters above sea level (masl)
From the top of the mountain you can enjoy views of Mount Sindoro, Mount Sumbing and Mount Merapi from a distance decorated with a sea of ​​​​mist. Mount Prau, the door to heaven, the peak of Dieng. When it's sunny, we will see a golden light that slowly rises and illuminates the hill of teletubbies
